trans-unit.source: Abstract class that, when implemented, defines an animation segment with its own target value and interpolation method for a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 구현 된 경우는 추상 클래스를 고유한 대상 값과 보간 메서드로 애니메이션 세그먼트 정의 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Int32KeyFrame is an abstract class that defines <xref:System.Int32> value type key frames for several different techniques of key frame animation: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: 정의 하는 추상 클래스 Int32KeyFrame <xref:System.Int32>값 형식을 여러 가지 방법 키 프레임 애니메이션에 대 한: <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: To animate a <xref:System.Int32> value with key frames, you define a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames> animation, and populate its <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A> property with one or more elements that define the key frames.
trans-unit.target: 애니메이션 효과를 주는 <xref:System.Int32>값 키 프레임을 사용 하 여 정의할는 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames>애니메이션 채웁니다 해당 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A>키 프레임을 정의 하는 하나 이상의 요소를 사용 하 여 속성.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames.KeyFrames%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Int32AnimationUsingKeyFrames> </xref:System.Int32>

trans-unit.source: For XAML syntaxes that take a Int32KeyFrame, you need to specify a non-abstract derived type of Int32KeyFrame as an object element.
trans-unit.target: Int32KeyFrame를 사용 하는 XAML 구문에 대 한 개체 요소로 Int32KeyFrame의 비추상 파생된 형식에 지정 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: For details, see the XAML syntax on the reference pages for <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.
trans-unit.target: 자세한 내용은, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame> <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.SplineInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.LinearInt32KeyFrame> ,</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.EasingInt32KeyFrame> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.DiscreteInt32KeyFrame> 참조 페이지의 XAML 구문 참조
